Achievements.Name: Moonshot!
Achievements.Description: Hit a mammoth 450+ foot home run.

Achievements.Name: Super Slugger
Achievements.Description: Hit 3 home runs in one game with the same player on "Pro" or higher difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Offensive Explosion
Achievements.Description: Score 20 runs in one game on "Pro" or higher difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: 5 Hit Game
Achievements.Description: Have a player get 5 base hits in one game.

Achievements.Name: Closing Time
Achievements.Description: Have a pitcher record a "save" by coming into a close ballgame to finish off a win.

Achievements.Name: Payoff
Achievements.Description: Make 10 successful "Payoff Pitches" in one game.

Achievements.Name: Strikeout the Side
Achievements.Description: Strike out all 3 batters you face in an inning.

Achievements.Name: Unhittable
Achievements.Description: Strikeout 15 batters with one pitcher on "Pro" or higher difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Thief
Achievements.Description: Successfully steal 2 bases in a game with one player.

Achievements.Name: Double Steal
Achievements.Description: Make a successful double steal (2 players steal a base on the same play)

Achievements.Name: Organized Crime
Achievements.Description: Have your team successfully steal 6 bases in one game.

Achievements.Name: Robbery!
Achievements.Description: Make a wall climb catch (rob a home run.)

Achievements.Name: Triple Double
Achievements.Description: Turned 3 double plays in one game.  "Triple Double" done baseball style.

Achievements.Name: Strikeout Leader
Achievements.Description: During a season, franchise, or GM Career, have a pitcher lead his league in strikeouts.

Achievements.Name: Home Run Leader
Achievements.Description: During a season, franchise, or GM Career, have a player lead the league in HRs.

Achievements.Name: Cy Young Winner
Achievements.Description: During a season, franchise, or GM Career, have a player win the Cy Young award.

Achievements.Name: World Series Winner
Achievements.Description: Play through a season (offline) and win the World Series.

Achievements.Name: Trivia Time
Achievements.Description: Successfully answer a trivia question between innings of a ball game.

Achievements.Name: League Participation
Achievements.Description: Play at least one game in an online league or tournament.

Achievements.Name: Get Connected
Achievements.Description: Play a full 9 inning game versus an online opponent

Achievements.Name: Win 10 Online
Achievements.Description: Win ten 9 inning games online.

Achievements.Name: 3-Game Streak
Achievements.Description: Go on a 3-game winning streak online.

Achievements.Name: 5-Game Streak
Achievements.Description: Go on a 5-game winning streak online.

Achievements.Name: Win 20 Online
Achievements.Description: Win twenty 9 inning games online.

Achievements.Name: Join Up
Achievements.Description: Join an online league or tournament.

Achievements.Name: No-Hitter
Achievements.Description: Pitched a complete game no-hitter.

Achievements.Name: Online Champion
Achievements.Description: Won an online tourney/league. Most impressive.

Achievements.Name: MVP Winner
Achievements.Description: Won the league MVP award.

Achievements.Name: Rail Lean Catch
Achievements.Description: Made an acrobatic catch leaning over foul territory railing.

Achievements.Name: Burglar
Achievements.Description: Stole home plate. You the man.

Achievements.Name: Ejected!
Achievements.Description: Ejected from a ballgame? Double Check!

Achievements.Name: Win 50 Online
Achievements.Description: Your dedication and skill are an inspiration to us all.

Achievements.Name: The Cycle
Achievements.Description: Hit a single, double, triple, and Home Run in one game with the same player. Astounding.
